\ul\fs28 Image Preprocessing \par
\ulnone\b0\fs22 Image Preprocessing are the steps we take to convert a raw image into an enhanced form that the model is ready to use for training and inference. The images collected for any computer vision tasks may be of different sizes, contrast, orientation.\par
\par
