\pard{\pntext\f3\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf3\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sl276\slmult1\b0 In digital image processing, histograms are used for simple calculations in software.\par
